---
description: Shared UI and component rules
globs:
  - "src/components/**/*.ts"
  - "src/components/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

UI rules:
- Prefer reusable primitives in src/components/ui
- Keep components small and composable
- Avoid mixing presentational concerns with business logic
- Do not create duplicate button, card, modal, or input patterns
- Keep the mobile UX simple and clear